        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The joint between the intake hose and either the air cleaner or the turbocharger inlet could be
                    compromised because of insufficient flexibility in the material. The improved material properties
                    and wall thickness of the replacement hose provide greater hose flexibility and joint integrity.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
